  <h2>Intake (CI/CD Webhooks)</h2>

  <p>
    Intake channels receive webhooks from CI/CD systems to automatically trigger
    deployments when builds complete.
  </p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Method</th><th>Path</th><th>Auth</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>GET</code></td><td><code>/api/intake/channels</code></td><td>Token</td><td>List configured intake channels</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST</code></td><td><code>/api/intake/channels</code></td><td>Token</td><td>Create a new intake channel (returns a webhook URL)</td></tr>
